{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_02_01",
  "title": "襲来！ボジミプロ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ハーハハハ！　星見プロは川咲さくらが乗っ取った！\nまずは{user}さんの椅子を奪ってやる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! Hoshimi Pro has been taken over by Sakura Kawasaki!\nFirst‚ I’m taking {user}-san’s chair!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.4999999841,
      "endTime": 12.4868934472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まれば、早速机の中を物色するのですわ！\n麻奈様のプレミアアイテムが見つかるかもしれません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s settled‚ then let’s rummage through the desks right away!\nWe might find one of Mana-sama’s premium items!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6868932565,
      "endTime": 21.4632650217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとさくら、すず。みんなが地方のお仕事で\n不在だからって調子に乗り過ぎよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Sakura‚ Suzu. Just because everyone’s away on regional jobs‚\ndon’t get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.676598088,
      "endTime": 27.7765982787,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6699.773716900001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6286.667029
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、勝手に机に座ったり引き出しを\n開けたり……変な物が出てきたらどうするの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ sitting at desks and opening drawers without permission…\nWhat if something weird comes out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.963265117,
      "endTime": 36.1523580392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "へ、へ、変な物……！？　それってもしかして\nちょっとエッチな雑誌とか……！？　キャー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-weird stuff…!? You don’t mean—\nl-like slightly naughty magazines…!? Kyaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3523581346,
      "endTime": 44.493242343300004,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8457.347003599998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ほらみんな、遊んでないで\nもう施錠するから事務所を出るわよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ everyone‚ stop fooling around.\nI’m locking up‚ so let’s head out of the office~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6799088956,
      "endTime": 50.9624237538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ゲシゲシゲシゲシ……おいで……おいで……\nこっちにおいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geshi-geshi-geshi-geshi… come here… come here…\nCome this way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1690904778,
      "endTime": 61.1624293488,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14373.945959300003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "おい！　さっきからゲシゲシゲシゲシうるさい！\n夜の配信に変な声入ったんだけど！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! That “geshi-geshi-geshi-geshi” has been noisy for a while now!\nA weird voice got into the night stream‚ you know!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3690960727,
      "endTime": 68.2280531726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "騒いではいたけど、ゲシゲシなんて言ってないわよね？\n確か向こうの方から、変な声が聞こえたような気が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were making noise‚ sure‚ but no one said “geshi-geshi‚” right?\nI think I heard a strange voice coming from over there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4347198012,
      "endTime": 78.7478261473,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16741.652003699997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、泥棒……とか！？　見に行ってみよう！\n……って、えぇぇぇぇぇぇぇ！？　これは……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be… a burglar!? Let’s go check it out!\n…Wait—EHHHHHH!? This is…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9478261473,
      "endTime": 90.6431756498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "観念しろ、川咲さくら！　これでもくらえ～！\nゲーシゲシゲシゲシ！　ゲーシゲシゲシゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Give it up‚ Sakura Kawasaki! Take this—!\nGeee-shi geshi geshi! Geee-shi geshi geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8298423928,
      "endTime": 99.7402275246,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_biglight-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3546.5294120999997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_biglight-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8966.67277009999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぎゃぁぁぁぁぁぁぁ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaahhhhhhh!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7965151629,
      "endTime": 103.46667277019999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Next Morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3333328247,
      "endTime": 105.5666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいなぁ……もう打ち合わせの時間なのに\nさくら達が見当たらないぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s strange… it’s already time for the meeting.\nBut Sakura and the others are nowhere to be seen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4793193418,
      "endTime": 112.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシゲシ！　ゲーシゲシゲシゲシ！\nお前が星見プロ、伝説のマネージャーゲシか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geee-shi geshi geshi! Geee-shi geshi geshi!\nAre you the legendary manager of Hoshimi Pro‚ geshi!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5716543434,
      "endTime": 120.96499330969999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "み、耳元で声が……！　……って、うわぁ！\n肩に小さいさくらが乗ってるぞ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A voice—right by my ear…! Wait—whoa!\nThere’s a tiny Sakura on my shoulder!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1716599383,
      "endTime": 127.21165684840001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ゲシィ！？　失礼ゲシね！\n私はさくらなどという珍妙な名前ではないゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "geshi!? How rude‚ geshi!\nI do not have the odd name “Sakura‚” geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4049902199,
      "endTime": 134.3649843453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私達はパラレルワールド『ボジミプロ』から\nやって来たアイドルゲシ！　お前達ー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are idols from the parallel world “Bojimi Pro‚”\nwho have come here‚ geshi! Come on guys—!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5716507831,
      "endTime": 140.8122461716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あんちゃん、うだつの上がらん顔しとんなぁ……\nまぁええわ、オグヤマズミレや、覚えとき！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey bro‚ you’ve got a pretty down-in-the-dumps face…\nWell‚ whatever—name’s Oguyama Zumire. Remember it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8050009009,
      "endTime": 153.6849979635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "オデ……ニダイメボジブルギゼギ……\nナルミヤズズ……ダス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am… second-generation Zudarry Biragle…\nZuzu Narumiya…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8716645158,
      "endTime": 160.71834234370002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "speakerNameEn": "gana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみませんすみませんすみません！\nゴジマガナ……です……ひぃっ！　忘れて大丈夫です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry‚ sorry‚ sorry!\nI’m Gana Gojima… eek! You can forget me‚ it’s fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9050090389,
      "endTime": 169.62501817499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ガンザギビボでーっす、きゃぴっ！　……なーんだ\nこの人全然イケてないぢゃーん。テンサゲ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Bibo Ganzagi—kyapi! …Huh?\nThis guy’s not cool at all. Total mood killer~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8383515275,
      "endTime": 178.7250171578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ズズ！？　ガナ！？　ガンザギビボ！？　なんで\nみんな濁点が付いてるんだ！？　呼びにくいだろ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zuzu!? Gana!? Ganzagi Bibo!?\nWhat’s with these names!? They’re hard to say!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9383505102,
      "endTime": 186.4935432669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "フッ……ナガゼゴドノ。人呼んで『輝き過ぎた輝き』さ\n私の輝かんばかりの美しさに見惚れないでおくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph… Godono Nagase. They call me “The Brilliance That Shines Too Much.”\nTry not to be dazzled by my overwhelming beauty…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.6935430762,
      "endTime": 198.620236325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "得意料理はチキン南蛮！　ボジミプロでは俺が参謀！\nザエギバルゴだYO！　エ～イ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My specialty’s chicken nanban! At Bojimi Pro‚ I’m the strategist!\nI’m Barugo Zaegi‚ YO! Ayy~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.8269028582,
      "endTime": 205.9802434839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
